{"tid":886082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子生殖器塗花生醬　狗狗整根咬斷吃掉後遭撲殺","createTime":"2018-11-02T00:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T13:32:27.000Z","uid":72009,"like":612,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"758f4b8fe5c226ef29455535e89324fc5cb223c2","tid":886082,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:21:25.000Z","msg":"英國蘇格蘭一名22歲男子，生殖器遭自家狗狗整根咬斷吃掉，男子一度陷入昏迷，與死神搏鬥。事後警方發現，男子在生殖器上塗抹花生醬，誘發狗狗攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，這名男子在生殖器上塗抹花生醬或其他食物，並引來自家鬥牛犬「大個子小子 (Biggie Smalls)」的攻擊。狗狗把男子的陰莖整根咬斷並吃掉，男子被發現時已經倒在血泊中，整個人陷入昏迷，一度與死神搏鬥。幸好男子經治療後，現已恢復意識，但陰莖已經接不回去，恐終身成為太監。<br />\n警方表示，一開始以為男子遭到友人打鬥撂倒，但之後證實事發當時，男子只和「大個子小子」在一起，相信牠是單獨犯案。警方也指出，之後在男子的同意下，大個子小子遭人道毀滅撲殺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181102/1458838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181102%2F1458838&d=J6RhEfzMus7NitM9hdRZVE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=72b43403\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181102%2F1458838&h=e5fc2ce4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181102/1458838</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181102/640_4f3ec4c70f76247637cce365832bca14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181102%2F640_4f3ec4c70f76247637cce365832bca14.jpg&h=c3c5be79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00893f85c3fb6703ccbc08e610f2569a9f17e951","tid":886082,"uid":23411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3cff3c5fd290e14b212d4cd73895b6ad7ae9b88","tid":886082,"uid":60655,"like":753,"dislike":1,"score":752,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:22:40.000Z","msg":"花式撚狗"},{"pid":"f2e37ddfc6a61fe899b79b0cb59fa3a02ea5